The following companies may have
unusual price changes in Spanish trading. Stock symbols are in
parentheses and share prices are from the previous close.  Spain ’s IBEX 35 added 1.9 percent to 10,132.60.  Portugal ’s
PSI 20 gained 0.8 percent to 7,338.01.  Abertis Infraestructuras SA (ABE)  : Salvador Alemany,
chairman of the Spanish highway operator, is scheduled to speak
at a conference in Barcelona. Abertis shares gained 1.1 percent
to 15.69 euros.       Actividades de Construccion y Servicios SA (ACS SM):
Analysts at UniCredit initiated coverage of the Spanish builder
with a “buy” rating. The shares rose 1.8 percent to 31.92
euros.  Inditex SA (ITX)  : The owner of the Zara fashion chain is
scheduled to report first-quarter earnings before the market
open. The shares added 1.1 percent to 61.75 euros.  To contact the reporter on this story:
